<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= clanci[0].naslov %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: lightgrey; /* Tamno siva pozadina */
            color: #fff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        tekst{
            color:green;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-dark">

<nav class="custom-navbar">
    <div class="custom-navbar-container">
        <div class="kao-logo">
            <a href="/">HakatonNovine.ba</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="custom-nav-links mt-3">
            <li><a href="/view/Kultura">Kultura</a></li>
            <li><a href="/view/Sport">Sport</a></li>
            <li><a href="/view/Tehnologija">Tehnologija</a></li>
            <li><a href="/view/Auto">Automobilizam</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="custom-search-container">
            <form action="/search" method="POST">
                <input id ="nesta" name="nesta" type="text" placeholder="Search..." class="custom-search-bar">
                <button type = "submit" class="custom-search-btn">üîç</button></form>
            <div class="korisnik-navbar">
                <a href="/users/Profile"><div class="log_in_dugme "> </div></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="container py-5">
    <!-- Back Button -->
    <div class="mb-4">
        <a href="/" class="btn dugme_za_nazad" style="background-color: #b63e3e;">&larr; Nazad na poƒçetak</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Article Header -->
    <div class="card bg-light text-dark text-light ">
        <div class="naslov_clanak card-header text-center  text-dark"style="background-color: rgba(182,62,62,0.8); border-color:rgba(255,62,62,1);" >
            <h1><%= clanci[0].naslov %></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Image Section -->
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                    <div
                            class="article-image"
                            style="
                                background-image: url('/<%= clanci[0].slika %>');
                                background-size: cover;
                                background-position: center;
                                height: 300px; border-radius: 12px;
                            "
                    ></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Article Info Section -->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <ul class="list-group " style="background-color: rgba(163,0,27,0.6)">
                        <li class="list-group-item text-dark">
                            <strong>Kategorija:</strong> <%= clanci[0].kategorija %>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item  text-dark">
                            <strong>Datum:</strong> <%= new Date(clanci[0].datum).toLocaleDateString() %>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item  text-dark">
                            <button class="btn btn-danger" onclick="Koment(<%=clanci[0].id %>)">Komentari</button>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Article Content -->
    <div class="card mt-4 bg-light text-dark " style="border-color:rgba(163,0,27,1)">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="tekst" style="color:rgba(163,0,27,1);">Vi≈°e informacija</h2>
            <p><%= clanci[0].artikal %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<footer class ="footer">
    <div class="container text-center py-3">

        <p>&copy; 2025 All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Hakaton iz predmeta Odabranih poglavlja kompjuterskih nauka</p>
        <p>Naziv projekta: Hakathon novine.  Datum hakatona : 17.1.2025.</p>
        <p>Studenti: Faris Lindov i Edah ≈Ωdraloviƒá</p>
    </div>
</footer>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script>
    function Koment(id){
        window.location.href = '/Komentari/Clanak/'+ id;
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>